nodes.text: Whyren's Reserve was a alcoholic beverage. The pirate Hondo Ohnaka once possessed six Whyren's Reserve bottles of sixteenth vintage, which Bar the Rotter consumed to drink himself to sleep. Cid's Parlor, a bar in Ord Mantell City, had Whyren's Reserve available for purchase amidst its various offerings. It was sold in a green bottle with a large aurek on the label. Multiple bottles of the drink were arranged on the shelves behind the bar.

Whyren's Reserve is mentioned in Star Wars: Smuggler's Guide, written by Daniel Wallace and first published in 2018. It made its first full appearance in the Star Wars: The Bad Batch episode "Rampage", which aired on May 28, 2021.
